<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idefaef4d5-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s3415"><num value="3415">§ 3415.</num><heading> Regulations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary is authorized to issue such regulations as may be necessary to carry out the provisions of this chapter.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idefaef4d6-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/pl/95/113/tXVII/s1716">Pub. L. 95–113, title XVII, § 1716</ref>, <date date="1977-09-29">Sept. 29, 1977</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/91/1040">91 Stat. 1040</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
